<article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" id="post-485265" class="post-485265 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-laser-hacks category-the-hackaday-prize tag-2021-hackaday-prize tag-galvanometer-laser-projection tag-piezo-actuator tag-vector-graphics">
    <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name">Laser Augmented Reality Glasses Show You The Way</h1>
        <div class="entry-meta">
            <a href="https://hackaday.com/2021/07/08/laser-augmented-reality-glasses-show-you-the-way/#respond" class="comments-counts"><span class="icon-hackaday icon-hackaday-comment"></span>
